const uzangibonga1Summary = '<p>\"Thatha lapha ubeke mntanami,\"wayetsho uMaGasela emqhubela i-album yezithombe. Walalamele wayamukela leyo album u- Bezel waseqala ukubuka izithombe ezaziphakathi.Zazingezomuntu oyedwa,isiphalaphala sentombi,zibukisakusukela leyo ntombi iselusane oluphathwayo,iphethwe nguyise lonina,unina kunguMagasela, ikhasa, ibe qotshwana, isemfundweni ephansi esikolweni. Isamukela imivuzo yokuphumelela esikolweni, iphethe inkezo, isemjahweni wokugijima incintisana labelungu. Kwathatha isikhathi eside ukuthi ayiphutshe leyo album ngoba ezinye izithombe wayeziphinda-phinda ikahulu lapho leyontombi isikhulile ebuka amabele ayo ayemi ethe mpo, izihlathi zayo lembala yayo. Yayikhanga leyo ntombi futhi ikhanya izithobile. Ngaphandle kwe-album leyo kwakubhalwe ibizo lomniniyo ngamabala amakhulu.<br />\"MAYIBONGWE DUBE\'S ALBUM\"</p>';

const uzangibonga2Summary = '<p>Baphenduka ekhaya, uNkosinathi loNkosinesisa sebephumelele empilweni, babethengele labo ababondlayo izipho. Babehamba labomkabo. UmkaNkosinesisa waguqa phambili kukaMaSibanda ephethe isipho wathi, \"Ngiyabonga mama, wangondlela umkami kuhle ekhula, wamfundisa impilo. Ngihlezi ngokuthula laye.\" Wahlengezela izinyembezi uMaSibanda. Inkosikazi kaNkosinathi layo yaguqa phambili kukaKhabo igebise ikhanda iphethe isipho yathi, \"Yamukela lesi sipho baba, ngiyabonga ukuthi wangakhela indoda emadideni, ngihlezi laye kuhle kakhulu ngokuthula uNkosinathi.\"</p>';